law.text:
A dissolved limited partnership that has completed winding up shall deliver to the Secretary of State for filing a statement of cancellation that states:
The name of the limited partnership;
The date of filing of its initial certificate of limited partnership; and
Any other information as determined by the general partners filing the statement or by a person appointed pursuant to KRS 362.2-803(3) or (4).
law.history: Created 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 149, sec. 107, effective July 12, 2006.
